com%2Fshrm-discrimination-lawsuit-verdict-11-million-racism-retaliation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eordered%20to%20pay%20%2411.5%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20unrelated%20race%20discrimination%20and%20retaliation%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.vaed.587322%2Fgov.uscourts.vaed.587322.1.0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20complaint%3C%2Fa%3E%20alleges%20that%20in%20June%202024%2C%20SHRM%20offered%20Torres%20a%20role%20as%20a%20senior%20specialist%20in%20its%20product%20management%20department%20at%20its%20office%20in%20Alexandria%2C%20Virginia%2C%20then%20revoked%20the%20offer%20in%20July%20because%20she%20wanted%20to%20bring%20her%20dog%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETorres%20said%20SHRM's%20offer%20to%20accommodate%20her%20medical%20needs%20was%20to%20allow%20her%20to%20keep%20food%2C%20water%2C%20and%20an%20insulin%20pump%20at%20her%20desk%2C%20which%20she%20felt%20was%20insufficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20ready%20and%20able%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Torres%20said%20in%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider%20through%20her%20attorney.%20%26quot%3BThey%20said%20they%20were%20eager%20to%20have%20me%20until%20they%20found%20out%20I%20had%20a%20disability%20and%20a%20service%20dog.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20quotes%20an%20email%20from%20SHRM%20to%20Torres%20denying%20her%20accommodation%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%5BI%5Dt%20does%20not%20appear%20there%20are%20any%20reasonable%20accommodations%20that%20would%20allow%20you%20to%20perform%20the%20essential%20functions%20of%20the%20role%2C%26quot%3B%20SHRM%20wrote%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESHRM%20spokesman%20Eddie%20Burke%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20specifics%20of%20the%20suit%2C%20saying%20the%20organization%20was%20still%20reviewing%20the%20legal%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20support%20the%20ADA%20and%20are%20actively%20committed%20to%20supporting%20employees%20through%20fair%2C%20respectful%2C%20and%20legally%20compliant%20accommodation%20processes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20fully%20complied%20with%20the%20ADA%20in%20this%20matter%20and%2C%20in%20consultation%20with%20outside%20legal%20counsel%2C%20met%20all%20of%20our%20obligations%20to%20provide%20reasonable%20accommodations%20to%20Fiona%20Torres.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELori%20Kisch%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20Torres%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20SHRM's%20alleged%20conduct%20was%20%26quot%3Bironic%26quot%3B%20given%20that%20it%20provides%20information%20and%20resources%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshrm-discrimination-case-hr-expertise-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20HR%20professionals%20follow%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20the%20ADA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20can't%20argue%20that%20they%20don't%20understand%20the%20law%2C%20and%20their%20actions%20are%20a%20reckless%20indifference%20to%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETorres'%20case%2C%20filed%20in%20federal%20court%20in%20Virginia%2C%20follows%20a%20lawsuit%20brought%20by%20a%20former%20SHRM%20employee%20that%20alleged%20race%20discrimination%20and%20retaliation.%20Rehab%20Mohamed%2C%20a%20Black%20and%20Egyptian%20instructional%20designer%2C%20claimed%20her%20SHRM%20manager%20held%20her%20to%20higher%20standards%20than%20white%20employees.%20A%20jury%20found%20SHRM%20liable%20for%20%2411.5%20million%20in%20damages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESHRM%20has%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20file%20an%20appeal%20and%20that%20the%20verdict%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20reflect%20the%20facts%2C%20the%20law%2C%20or%20the%20truth%20of%20how%26quot%3B%20it%20operates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhr-giant-shrm-faces-new-discrimination-lawsuit-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22