0day.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20could%20introduce%20a%2023-hour%20trading%20session%20in%202026%20if%20the%20SEC%20approves%20its%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFinance%20pros%20are%20mixed.%20It%20could%20enable%20more%20people%20to%20trade%2C%20but%20also%20lead%20to%20a%20more%20uneven%20playing%20field.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20major%20shift%20may%20be%20coming%20for%20the%20stock%20market%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENasdaq%20is%20planning%20to%20submit%20paperwork%20to%20the%20Securities%20%26amp%3B%20Exchange%20Commission%20seeking%20approval%20to%20enable%20around-the-clock%20stock%20trading%20for%2023%20hours%20a%20day%20during%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20would%20shake%20up%20the%20long-standing%209%3A30%20a.m.%20to%204%20p.m.%20trading%20session%20that's%20been%20in%20place%20since%20the%201980s%2C%20and%20market%20pros%20have%20mixed%20views%20on%20the%20prospect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20market%20veterans%20believe%20that%20around-the-clock%20trading%20would%20ultimately%20be%20beneficial%20for%20the%20market%2C%20others%20have%20raised%20concerns%20that%20the%20move%20could%20lead%20to%20an%20uneven%20playing%20field%20or%20gamify%20equities%20in%20a%20way%20that%20makes%20the%20market%20resemble%20crypto%20more%20closely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobinhood%20already%20has%2024-hour%20markets%20for%20some%20popular%20stocks%2C%20and%20crypto%20markets%20famously%20trade%2024%2F7.%20Some%20argue%20that%20the%20added%20trading%20hours%20make%20these%20assets%E2%80%94particularly%20crypto%2C%20which%20often%20sees%20big%20swings%20over%20the%20weekend%E2%80%94more%20volatile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20the%20pros%20are%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227e5d39c6-fc27-4c71-9eb8-5ecd3b17f2dd%5C%22%3EThe%20case%20for%20a%2023-hour%20trading%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20selling%20point%20of%20Nasdaq's%20around-the-clock%20trading%20initiative%20is%20that%20it%20could%20help%20democratize%20markets%20and%20make%20trading%20more%20accessible%2C%20particularly%20to%20traders%20outside%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJos%C3%A9%20Torres%2C%20a%20senior%20economist%20at%20Interactive%20Brokers%2C%20said%20that%20many%20people%20who%20want%20to%20trade%20stocks%20find%20it%20difficult%20if%20they%20work%20a%20normal%209-5%20job%20or%20live%20outside%20the%20US.%20Extending%20the%20trading%20day%20would%20address%20both%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20gives%20greater%20access%20for%20more%20participation%20across%20demographics%2C%20across%20applications%2C%20across%20geographies%2C%26quot%3B%20Torres%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20it's%20also%20good%20because%20it'll%20offer%20real-time%20looks%20and%20real-time%20reactions%20on%20things%20that%20are%20happening%20overnight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sentiment%20was%20echoed%20by%20Bob%20Lange%2C%20founder%20and%20chief%20options%20analyst%20of%20options%20trading%20and%20education%20platform%20Explosive%20Options.%20He%20said%20he%20sees%20the%20move%20as%20ultimately%20positive%2C%20as%20it%20will%20likely%20enable%20more%20people%20to%20start%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227777e814-18d6-4401-8fee-39ee542df10f%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20the%20cons%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20Torres%20nor%20Lange%20is%20concerned%20about%20more%20trading%20causing%20volatility%20in%20markets%20to%20increase.%20That%20said%2C%20Lange%20said%20he%20sees%20other%20potential%20problems%20developing%20if%20the%20Nasdaq%20introduces%20longer%20trading%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20believe%20that%20the%20smart%20money%20is%20going%20to%20really%20participate%20in%20this%2C%20in%20this%20after-hours%20trading%20market%2C%20per%20se%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20volume%20is%20just%20not%20going%20to%20be%20big%20enough%20to%20create%20a%20very%20fair%20market%20for%20individuals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Ashley%20Schulman%2C%20CIO%20of%20Running%20Point%20Capital%20Advisors%2C%20said%