Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERashel%20Hariri%2C%20a%20founder%20and%20podcast%20host%2C%20uses%20ChatGPT%20to%20create%20personalized%2C%20intentional%20gifts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20builds%20profiles%20and%20uses%20her%20own%20framework%20to%20tailor%20gifts%20to%20each%20person.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20the%20approach%20saves%20time%2C%20reduces%20decision%20fatigue%2C%20and%20helps%20her%20give%20better%20gifts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Rashel%20Hariri%2C%20a%2038-year-old%20founder%20and%20host%20of%20%26quot%3BShe's%20Interesting%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20lives%20in%20Arkansas.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20shown%20care%20through%20gift-giving.%20When%20I%20choose%20something%20for%20someone%2C%20I%20want%20them%20to%20feel%20seen%20and%20have%20something%20they'll%20actually%20use.%20I'm%20not%20someone%20who%20is%20going%20to%20give%20luxurious%2C%20massive%20gifts%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20gifts%20I%20give%20are%20meaningful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20year%2C%20AI%20has%20become%20the%20most%20effective%20way%20for%20me%20to%20do%20that.%20ChatGPT%20has%20become%20like%20a%20gifting%20concierge%2C%20helping%20me%20organize%20my%20brainstorming%20and%20land%20on%20presents%20that%20feel%20thoughtful%2C%20personal%2C%20and%20aligned%20with%20someone's%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aaf204ae-2839-450a-8144-1d2b26c6957f%5C%22%3EI%20developed%20a%20framework%20for%20what%20makes%20a%20good%20gift%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20conversations%20with%20the%20women%20in%20my%20podcast%20community%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frashelhariri.com%2Fpodcast%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShe's%20Interesting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20realized%20that%20people%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20women%20in%20their%2030s%20like%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20value%20three%20main%20things%3A%20gifts%20that%20feel%20a%20little%20luxurious%2C%20gifts%20that%20expand%20our%20brains%20(like%20books%20or%20courses)%2C%20and%20gifts%20that%20make%20the%20day-to-day%20easier.%20This%20became%20my%20three-part%20framework%20for%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20information%2C%20I%20started%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.openai.com%2Fen%2Farticles%2F10169521-projects-in-chatgpt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproject%20in%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20creates%20a%20space%20to%20group%20similar%20chats%20around%20the%20gifting%20topic%20%E2%80%94%20and%20provided%20custom%20instructions%20for%20the%20AI%20to%20follow%2C%20like%20background%20information%20on%20my%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20create%20your%20own%20framework%2C%20think%20about%20what's%20most%20important%20to%20you%20and%20the%20people%20around%20you.%20What%20makes%20you%20the%20happiest%3F%20What%20types%20of%20things%20make%20your%20life%20easier%3F%20Use%20the%20answers%20to%20those%20questions%20as%20main%20points%20in%20your%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22572%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20conversation%20with%20ChatGPT%20about%20what%20types%20of%20gifts%20to%20give%20friends%20and%20family%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6942ea5264858d02d216f9bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECreate%20a%20project%20in%20ChatGPT%20to%20organize%20similar%20topics%20and%20ideas.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20courtesy%20of%20Rashel%20Hariri%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f1141cf-90bf-4b29-8cc0-42540990e1b2%5C%22%3EI%20started%20an%20ongoing%20conversation%20for%20each%20recipient%20in%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20my%20ChatGPT%20project%2C%20I%20have%20separate%20conversations%20for%20each%20of%20the%20people%20I'm%20shopping%20for%3A%20my%20husband%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20start%20by%20describing%20each%20person%2C%20including%20basic%20demographics%2C%20as%20well%20as%20deeper%20information%2C%20such%20as%20what's%20important%20to%20them%2C%20their%20likes%20and%20dislikes%2C%20personal%20goals%2C%20and%20things%20they're%20struggling%20with.%20I%20might%20also%20include%20their%20astrological%20sign%20and%20their%20favorite%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20to%20be%20someone%20who%20pays%20attention%20to%20your%20friends%2C%20because%20otherwise%2C%20AI%20will%20give%20you%20basic%20suggestions.%20I%20try%20to%20give%20ChatGPT%20everything%20I%20know%20about%20the%20person.%20If%20I%20have%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20friend%20or%20family%20member%20and%20something%20stands%20out%2C%20I%20can%20go%20into%20the%20chat%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BTake%20note%20that%20this%20person%20said%20X.%26quot%3B%20The%20more%20I%20use%20it%2C%20the%20more%20it%20learns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it's%20time%20to%20buy%20a%20gift%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20months%20later%2C%20all%20those%20details%20are%20stored.%20It's%20a%20mental%20relief%2C%20like%20your%20notes%20app%2C%20but%20way%20smarter%20because%20it%20responds%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20of%20that%20information%20uploaded%2C%20I%20prompt%20ChatGPT%20to%20come%20up%20with%20gift%20ideas%20within%20my%20framework%20for%20each%20person.%20You%20can%20also%20give%20it%20a%20specific%20budget%20to%20work%20within.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20comes%20up%20with%20initial%20ideas%20and%20explains%20why%20each%20gift%20works%20for%20the%20recipient.%20From%20there%2C%20it%20becomes%20a%20conversation%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20like%20talking%20to%20the%20person%20I'm%20shopping%20for.%20I%20might%20ask%20for%20more%20ideas%20within%20a%20category%2C%20or%20the%20ideas%20might%20remind%20me%20of%20something%20else%20about%20the%20person%2C%20and%20I'll%20ask%20it%20to%20generate%20new%20suggestions%20with%20that%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fae9aa3c-3197-4775-bb15-683428dce3bf%5C%22%3EI%20still%20make%20the%20final%20gift%20decision%2C%20but%20ChatGPT%20can%20be%20speedy%20and%20creative%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20brainstorm%20all%20of%20this%20myself%2C%20but%20AI%20has%20made%20the%20process%2060%20to%2070%25%20faster%2C%20and%20given%20me%20a%20tool%20I%20can%20return%20to%20for%20future%20gift%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20choose%20the%20final%20gifts%20to%20give%2C%20but%20if%20I'm%20feeling%20stuck%20between%20ideas%2C%20I'll%20go%20back%20to%20ChatGPT%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BHere%20are%20two%20items%20I'm%20deciding%20between.%20Help%20me%20narrow%20it%20down.%26quot%3B%20It%20asks%20me%20questions%20to%20help%20decide%3A%20Does%20she%20need%20this%3F%20What's%20her%20plan%20for%20the%20next%20three%20months%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20often%20makes%20suggestions%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20thought%20of.%20I%20told%20ChatGPT%20about%20a%20friend%20who%20struggles%20to%20find%20any%20time%20for%20himself%20while%20balancing%20a%20busy%20career%20and%20two%20kids.%20The%20tool%20recommended%20%26quot%3BThe%20Five-Minute%20Journal.%26quot%3B%20He%20loved%20it%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20thoughtful%20and%20tailored.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20of%20gift-giving%20is%20that%20moment%20when%20someone%20opens%20it%20and%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20God%2C%20you%20know%20me%20so%20well!%26quot%3B%20We%20want%20to%20give%20the%20people%20we%20love%20something%20that%20makes%20them%20feel%20good%2C%20and%20this%20process%20has%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-gift-guide-ai-to-plan-presents-holiday-season-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1766079364000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6942f21d64858d02d216faeb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-gift-guide-ai-to-plan-presents-holiday-s